user_prompt_template:
LIFE EVENT: {life_event}
AUDIENCE: {audience}
TONE: {tone}
ADDITIONAL CONTEXT: {context}

Design a complete operational system for this life event. Every field is mandatory. Be specific to this exact life event — no generic frameworks.

Return ONLY the following JSON object. No prose. No markdown. No code fences.

{{
  "system_name": "A specific, named operational system — e.g. 'Estate Command System', 'Caregiver Protocol v1', 'Relocation Operations Hub'",
  "life_event": "The life event exactly as provided",
  "operating_premise": "One sentence: the core operational challenge this system addresses",
  "system_objective": "One sentence: the single measurable outcome this system achieves when fully executed",
  "time_horizon": "Estimated operational duration — e.g. '90 days', '6-18 months', 'Ongoing'",
  "control_domains": [
    {{
      "id": "domain-01",
      "name": "Domain name",
      "purpose": "What this domain governs",
      "scope_in": ["What is inside this domain"],
      "scope_out": ["What is explicitly excluded"],
      "primary_outputs": ["Tangible outputs this domain produces"]
    }}
  ],
  "key_roles": [
    {{
      "role": "Role name",
      "responsibility": "What this role owns and decides",
      "authority_level": "decision-maker | advisor | executor | observer"
    }}
  ],
  "critical_milestones": [
    {{
      "milestone": "Milestone name",
      "description": "What it means to reach this milestone",
      "sequence": 1
    }}
  ],
  "success_criteria": ["Specific, verifiable outcome — not vague goals"],
  "failure_modes": ["Specific ways this system could fail or derail"],
  "operating_constraints": ["Concrete constraints the system must operate within"]
}}
